title: The Circus - S01E21
description:
Series 1, Episode 21 of The Circus - the greatest political show on TV with a genuinely unique approach to covering this crazy election, getting access to the people that matter and really know politics. This week you get to see what news anchors really think of Trump, and analysis of how the Alicia Machado claims are handled.


For some reason the regular uploaders have slowed right down on this site- it's a real shame, I have had to scour all over to find these episodes.

The great news is that this week is that an HD version is available - massive thanks to esc & whoever else captured this this. Hopefully future episodes will be shared directly here in this format.


The Circus is essential viewing for every voter as it goes behind the spin and actually shines a light on the candidates - and voters should have access to it on a free to air network.

Sadly the show is taking a couple of weeks off, back in 3 weeks time
